'''蘇魯河'''（{{lang-en|Suru River}}；{{lang-ur|{{Nastaliq|سرو دریا}}}}），是[[印度河|印度河]]左岸支流，<ref name="suru indus">{{cite book | author=S. S. Negi | title=Cold Deserts of India | url=http://books.google.co.in/books?id=54RgJ6FgMl0C&pg=PA13&dq=suru+river+tributary+of+indus+river&output=html_text&cd=3 | accessdate=28 August 2012 | year=2002 | publisher=Indus Publishing, 2002 | isbn=9788173871276 | page=-13 | archive-date=2018-12-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181225113556/https://books.google.co.in/books?id=54RgJ6FgMl0C&pg=PA13&dq=suru+river+tributary+of+indus+river&output=html_text&hl=en | dead-url=no }}</ref>位於[[印度|印度]][[查謨-克什米爾邦|查謨-克什米爾邦]][[拉達克|拉達克]]地區[[卡基爾縣|卡基爾縣]]。

蘇魯河幹流長度{{convert|185|km}}，發源於{{link-en|潘昔拉山口|Pensi La}}附近的潘澤拉冰河。河源位於[[卡爾吉爾|卡爾吉爾]]南方約{{convert|142|km}}，[[藏斯卡|藏斯卡]]北方約{{convert|79|km}}處。蘇魯河形成藏斯卡山脈的西部及北部邊界。<ref name="zanskar range">{{Cite web|url=http://www.ladakh.com/ladakh-info/rivers|title=Rivers of Ladakh|publisher=ladakh.com|accessdate=2012-08-29|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120902233945/http://www.ladakh.com/ladakh-info/rivers|archivedate=2012-09-02}}</ref>

